{"tid":1563072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(緊急)應該要唱美國國歌，唔係願榮歸香港","createTime":"2019-09-12T09:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T12:52:47.000Z","uid":131157,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3bf1b87b27bdd593410be848f2cd91a8e22f6943","tid":1563072,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n據聞美國只需一位參議員提出senate hold，只要全體不足三分二反對，香港人權及民主法案即可在參議會上無限期擱置，直至有關議員收回動議。<br />\n<br />\n假如屬實，中國將全力收買部份參議員，企圖促成法案流產。與此同時，在香港營造萬人普天同慶唱流行曲的氣氛，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">將上周高舉美國國旗、唱美國國歌的勢頭消散於無形</span></span></strong>。只要香港人不再強烈請求美國支援，而香港事態不會影響美國的民主，美國將不會有動力以狠辣的法案監察香港。屆時，民意代表泛民議員將有充分的理由建議美國減辣，以免在局勢緩和的時候傷害香港經濟。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要未來兩周，香港人繼續以所謂香港國歌取代美國國歌的話，將美國角色隱沒至大後方的話，美國減辣的機會相當高。</span></strong>要保持辣度，必需仰賴美國議員極具說服力論證，非常困難。香港人將自己的好牌一張張的送出，無話可說。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157187675233880&amp;id=700268879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157187675233880%26id%3D700268879&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=2b198bb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157187675233880&amp;id=700268879</a>"},{"pid":"aba8556a623278acb96423da1dc53f2dfa65a313","tid":1563072,"uid":229385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:24:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7644dc28d695b52e0d9bfd99ac4eed50820b61df","tid":1563072,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:24:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e839c997053e4ee69b68d522e4c493e4825ffa24","tid":1563072,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8f5052f422771175b09050ac6c04d043a820a9","tid":1563072,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa